    "30 Since then, several researchers and experts have investigated the challenges of AI liability regimes.",
    "Currently, the EU tends to support the idea of strict liability for high-risk AI systems.",
    "That is because the existing legal framework, based on the PLD, has gaps [104].",
    "The PLD proposes a fault-based liability regime, although, since its establishment in 1985, it has not covered the new AI challenges within it.",
    "Following this investigation and its debates, the EU released a legislative proposal known as the AI Act in 2021."
